      "writtenOn": "2016-09-15T16:21:59Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Just want to note that appending this suffix will result in invalid builder names. I don\u0027t think anyone is parsing them after this point, so it probably doesn\u0027t matter, but might be worth considering changing to \"_NoBuildbot\".  It\u0027s also worth noting that we only need this because we currently have duplicate TaskSpec/Builder names.  If we transition intelligently, we could avoid that.",
